@startuml UEORMS_State_02
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 2) Subscription and Billing

[*] --> PlanBrowsing
PlanBrowsing --> TrialActive : start trial
PlanBrowsing --> SubscriptionActive : paid start
TrialActive --> SubscriptionActive : upgrade
SubscriptionActive --> SubscriptionChanged : change plan
SubscriptionChanged --> SubscriptionActive : cycle applied
SubscriptionActive --> InvoiceGenerated : billing run
InvoiceGenerated --> InvoiceSent : email invoice
InvoiceSent --> PaymentPending : due window
PaymentPending --> Paid : payment success
PaymentPending --> Failed : payment failed
Failed --> PaymentPending : retry
Paid --> SubscriptionActive : continue service
SubscriptionActive --> CancelRequested : request cancel
CancelRequested --> Cancelled : term end
Cancelled --> [*]

@enduml
